## Guardrails

- Do not run `npx -y agent-device@latest` unattended; use the globally installed or project-pinned CLI.
- Do not bypass login, passcode, payments, or privacy prompts — stop and ask the user.
- Capture screenshots, logs, recordings, and `.ad` replay scripts only when they add evidence; store under `docs/agent-device-artifacts/`.
- Physical iPhone recording is best-effort (not guaranteed 60 FPS); `open` the app before `record start`.

